data.description: Colonial style home located in Huntington on a double lot.  Almost an acre right in town, most of lot is completely fenced.  Remodeled kitchen with granite and stainless appliances.  Huge family room with built-ins, plus a bonus (playroom), formal living and dining, den with brick fireplace.  Owners suite is upstairs with lots of closet space.  Brick paver covered porch, 2 car attached carport, attached workshop and extra 10 x 10 storage shed.  Security system and sprinkler system with well.
